&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova light,arial nova light_embeddedfont,arial nova light_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Salgado-Maya remains in custody at the Marion County Jail. All further media inquiries should be directed to the Marion County District Attorney&rsquo;s Office.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova light,arial nova light_embeddedfont,arial nova light_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

