Location: Kalapuya Building, 4500 SW Research Way, Corvallis&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_M80TASJPSpyFIr6BlOUO-A#/registration"&gt;Zoom registration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

