Board of Commissioners adopts final written decision&lt;br /&gt;
Location: Kalapuya Building, 4500 SW Research Way, Corvallis&lt;br /&gt;
Visit the &lt;a href="https://boc.bentoncountyor.gov/events-calendar/"&gt;Board of Commissioners Meeting Portal&lt;/a&gt; to access a live stream of the meeting.&lt;/p&gt;

