&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The America 250 Oregon Commission is currently offering two traveling exhibitions that are&amp;nbsp;available to rent at no cost!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

