&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;The Lane County Sheriff&rsquo;s Office received assistance during this investigation from the Oregon Department of Justice, Oregon State Police, and Homeland Security Investigations (HSI). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
