&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SALEM, Ore. &mdash; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;A coordinated retail theft operation conducted Thursday at the Willamette Town Center resulted in multiple arrests and the recovery of stolen merchandise.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;On October 30, detectives from the Salem Police Department&rsquo;s Felony Crimes Unit, in partnership with the Violent Crimes Unit, Patrol Division, and loss prevention teams from TJ Maxx, Sierra, HomeGoods, and Burlington, conducted a targeted retail theft sting at the shopping center on Lancaster Drive NE. The operation was funded by the Oregon Department of Justice Organized Retail Theft Grant Program.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW101638079 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Over the course of the operation, seven individuals were arrested for various theft-related offenses. One individual was also charged with interfering with a peace officer and possession of fentanyl. Several outstanding arrest warrants were served. Approximately $1,000 in stolen merchandise was recovered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
