&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;On October 31st at about 12:45 p.m., a Lane County Sheriff&rsquo;s deputy driving a patrol vehicle was involved in a crash with another vehicle in the area of River Road and Maxwell Road, Eugene. The deputy and the driver of the other vehicle were both transported to an area hospital with non-life-threatening injuries. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
