&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to help feed our community:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;Donate nonperishable food at one of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://svzagddbb.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0017oDNtTpXD-iuJCYCSFGea1P3u1a8EZiMyh81dh12is-UCs8uxCJSIsQSejcbeC9T8mWpff0t_txKHdU_VZX_Z8t-59mDcISP8sbDsCUVy7sTSBcJU5CE66JK5RPXqep7yzsIEbqnNP5agOtPEmC-nVrQYoYL3hNY8HeatO5iBlBVPI4hQzbOI8abxwtk5S43n71CibLBzHv68n7L5CrB3bvjQBE-PfBhnvGSej4A5tVOlN0QoXNE1zMao3vTTZRND2aK8MSD1ZD6HsP6CCDBOg==&amp;amp;c=zKUx5pnIq-fqLkvHp2nTX-fKneH0A1zSRtyayDn2clUSeGLJiWMHeA==&amp;amp;ch=oNXi0zIimaU2-1_eyOtjXtrNPXb0EIR3d48swI_L3Ti7hD6Byvy_uA==" id="anchor-e75b65de-bea8-21f3-d062-723b5c0e2d50" style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;" title="https://svzagddbb.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0017oDNtTpXD-iuJCYCSFGea1P3u1a8EZiMyh81dh12is-UCs8uxCJSIsQSejcbeC9T8mWpff0t_txKHdU_VZX_Z8t-59mDcISP8sbDsCUVy7sTSBcJU5CE66JK5RPXqep7yzsIEbqnNP5agOtPEmC-nVrQYoYL3hNY8HeatO5iBlBVPI4hQzbOI8abxwtk5S43n71CibLBzHv68n7L5CrB3bvjQBE-PfBhnvGSej4A5tVOlN0QoXNE1zMao3vTTZRND2aK8MSD1ZD6HsP6CCDBOg==&amp;amp;c=zKUx5pnIq-fqLkvHp2nTX-fKneH0A1zSRtyayDn2clUSeGLJiWMHeA==&amp;amp;ch=oNXi0zIimaU2-1_eyOtjXtrNPXb0EIR3d48swI_L3Ti7hD6Byvy_uA=="&gt;local food banks listed here&lt;/a&gt;. There are food banks in Adair Village, Albany, Alsea, Blodgett, Corvallis, Monroe and Philomath.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://communityservices.us/linn-benton-food-share/" id="anchor-d3e02714-9c32-6e74-da57-b8665ae99ff9" style="border: 0px; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;" title="https://communityservices.us/linn-benton-food-share/"&gt;Donate funds to Linn Benton Food Share&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to provide the equivalent of six meals for every dollar donated.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;Volunteer at a food bank or meal site. There are many volunteer opportunities at local soup kitchens and food pantries. In addition, Linn Benton Food Share needs volunteers to repackage food, glean surplus food from farmers and grocers, host or participate in a food drive/fundraiser, help with special events and more. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

