&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;&ldquo;We&rsquo;re a family here,&rdquo; Chief Tacy said. &ldquo;Our firefighters, medics, and staff show up every day with professionalism and compassion. I&rsquo;m honored to continue that legacy.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
